lead_paragraph: An Olympic gold medal was not the pinnacle of the sport for golfers according to world number four Rory McIlroy, and he had no concerns about his decision to withdraw from the Rio de Janeiro Games.

headline.print_headline: Golfers Dream of Green Jackets, Not Olympic Gold: McIlroy
